author: Brian Markey
reviewBody: Not Verified |  Great airport. Easy to park, easy to get to terminal and fast security. Beats almost every other larger airport I have been to. Not much to do but you won't be there long anyway.

author: Daniel Mcgarity
reviewBody: A fine small airport, great personal service, clean, well decorated, easy parking, simple and efficient signage, has a luxury feel befitting the Palm Beach Clientele. Food selection adequate and reasonable. Parking is a breeze. Always many security personnel and queue times very short. A pleasure to travel to or from.
